data.description: Four Bedroom Four level split with lots of space to enjoy your family. More square footage finished than on assessors page. This home has a great family room with wood burning FPLC ,  Main level is the living room, formal dining room and kitchen. Also walks out to a large deck and fenced back yard with an above ground pool measuring (13x21) that will be amazing in the summer heat. Pantry cupboard in the kitchen for additional storage and a peninsula for breakfast seating. Upstairs there are 3 bedrooms and full bath. It is located on a corner lot, so very convenient.. The backyard area has an additional shed 12x18 and a new concrete slab 20x27. Basketball court area with a 18x17 slab of concrete ( the hoop stays) 1 Car oversize garage with epoxy coating. Mitchellville elementary school was also selected 6th best elementary school in Iowa per the U.S News & World Report! Make your move today!
